<div id="main">
  <div class="about">
    <h1>ABOUT ME</h1>
    <h2>
      {{#if isLoggedIn}}
        Hi,{{name}}! &nbsp; &nbsp;
      {{/if}}</h2>
    <br />
    <p>Hi, I'm Jie Chen, a second-year student at Jönköping University studying
      New Media Design. I'm passionate about creating digital experiences.
    </p>
    <br />
    <h2>I'm skilled in:</h2>
    {{#if isAdmin}}
      <div><a href="/skills/new" id="new" class="btn btn-link">NEW SKILLS</a></div>
    {{/if}}
    <ul>
      {{#each skills}}
        <li><a href="/projects/skills/{{sid}}">{{sname}}</a> - ({{spro}})</li>
        <div>
          {{#if ../isAdmin}}
            <a href="/skills/update/{{sid}}" id="modifySkill">Modify</a>
            <a href="/skills/delete/{{sid}}" id="deleteSkill">Delete</a>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>

    <br />
    <p>I love blending technology and creativity to craft engaging digital
      experiences. Let's work together to create something amazing!</p>
  </div>
</div>